## Summary

This documentation covers the Amplitude Experiment iOS SDK for client-side feature flag evaluation, including installation via CocoaPods/SPM, initialization with Amplitude Analytics or third-party integrations, remote/local evaluation methods (fetch/start), variant access with automatic exposure tracking, and provider interfaces for user management and exposure tracking.

